01:09:18.547 --> 01:09:19.380
Any other questions?

01:09:25.859 --> 01:09:28.520
OK, and so some other fact.

01:09:28.520 --> 01:09:32.170
And again, I will
just list them.

01:09:32.170 --> 01:09:33.859
I will just them.

01:09:33.859 --> 01:09:37.750
If you're not
